{
  "stem": "25831.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He set a tremendous example for me, but it boomeranged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I never followed in his-- I never adopted his work habits.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother took a one hour nap every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I always looked forward to her waking up because then we could play or do something, anything but homework.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had violin lessons, and she played piano moderately well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And accompanied me and was not very critical of me and-- Very often said, when I squeaked a little less, this is beautiful.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went out of the house too, and I played in the garden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kids dropped in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Friends of mine dropped in, and they loved to come to our house because my mother was very nice to them, unusually nice to all of them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had one friend-- and I now go to the year 1934-- I had one friend who was a Galician immigrant who didn't look clean.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father just couldn't stand him, and he didn't want him to come to the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the kid picked that up, my father's dislike for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One day when he was at our house, he cut himself on something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his finger began to bleed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my mother called, saw that and said, come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she took him to her room and washed the hand and administered to the finger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And afterward, he said to me, it was so nice of your mother to be so accepting of me, which is just terrible and which points to the great prejudice, unjustified prejudice, which many German Jews had to its eastern Jews.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was those who came from territories east of the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In America, fathers always try to be in touch with their children's feelings.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
